Step 1: Collect Text

Example:

Movie Reviews
Customer Reviews
Tweets
Emails
WhatsApp Messages
Step 2: Preprocessing

Input:

"I LOVE this Movie!!!"

After preprocessing:

love movie

Tasks include:

Lowercase
Remove punctuation
Remove stop words
Tokenization
Step 3: Tokenization

Sentence:

I love AI

Becomes

["I", "love", "AI"]
Step 4: Convert Words into Numbers

Computers understand numbers, not words.

Example

I      → 10
love   → 45
AI     → 62

or use embeddings:

love → [0.12, 0.67, 0.55 ...]

These numeric vectors capture semantic meaning.


